  "text": "The first reports of large-scale exome NGS in HNSCC [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] illustrated the lack of attention to intra-tumor genetic heterogeneity as recently as 5 years ago. They also, however, provided the information needed to develop a general way to measure that heterogeneity.",
